25/01/2009
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Bosnian police said on Friday (January 23rd) they have launched an investigation into death threats against one of the country's leading investigative journalists, Bakir Hadziomerovic. 
The journalist reported receiving threats at the beginning the month, as well as another one last Thursday. 
Hadziomerovic is known for his exposes of political links to organised crime. 
(AFP, DPA, BTA - 23/01/09)
